{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "3e36f48e-db3a-4968-b2ba-bab0affb5a8b",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 2 06 - Rune Null",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "1322ad5d-c08d-4725-be0a-5d6a5aff08c5",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "8210337a-2f6a-4576-9f9f-ed7bf871ecb4",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "59f2c44d-c573-44c5-9c4d-11ac68deb896",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For this class, we will be learning about the Null Rune and runestone. The Null runestone creates a field that blocks magic. It can be used as a shield against offensive spells.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "958e1f05-5ab9-49ec-b531-7e40627787ad",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The Null Rune will block any spell, even one cast by the Magic User who created the runestone. Thus, this runestone isn't commonly used by spellcasters, but should prove to be quite useful for mundane Magic Users such as yourselves.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "acb6f11c-a166-42c9-8c30-9f427bb70da8",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It takes a moderate amount of Mojo to activate the runestone once it is placed upon the ground.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "41eb6694-532c-43c2-b8c6-db74db62d9ff",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Since the Null runestone creates an active shield for magic, the effect will only last until that Mojo has been used, roughly about ten minutes after activating the runestone. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "54180499-4237-477d-a5a6-adbdce55fb75",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "7105a4f5-0eec-4f15-976e-43bcebd03dc7",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "26bcbe5b-df83-456d-b18e-f71288ade08f",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f1caf1d5-941e-4f39-87a3-9376750e71c3",
                            "text": "Ask About the Professor's Teaching Career",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7f0a2e08-0cbf-44e4-902b-40157bebf6c3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "How did you get involved in teaching? Wouldn't you rather be off doing wizardly things?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "27b2ae78-cd34-47e4-a863-9a65c7dc1153",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Not all Wizards are reclusive researchers who live in isolated towers or colleges.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "08277245-25ac-42af-9e17-d478de632236",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Most Wizards have to have some way to make a living. Some are consultants and advisors to kings and nobles. Some are spellcasters who help construct castles or bridges. Some are War Wizards or defenders.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7dd352b9-93af-4673-a559-f54eb9df783e",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I was working at the Wizard's Institute of Technocery as the librarian when my mentor Erasmus suggested that I might be interested in a teaching position at the <i>School for Heroes</i> in Silmaria.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4997aa30-2f82-4780-9d97-4215c7c4d1bf",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I've always been more of a people person than most Wizards. As it turns out, I discovered that I enjoy sharing my love and knowledge of magic. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "ae2d39b1-e981-44ac-a1a0-5116b460600a",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "68",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "909a6be2-11ae-4bef-a536-56dd2fe59e8b",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "8",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "974ce2b9-fd5d-479c-a153-c1c47d3391e8",
                            "text": "Ask About the Null Runestone and Mojo",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4ed2cadc-68d3-4dc7-a75f-cddb6fb49349",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What happens when a Null runestone uses up all the Mojo? Does it just stop working?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fd3043d9-8380-40f1-a84c-3963fd3a6e2b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, once a Null runestone has been activated, it uses the activation Mojo to power the spell. When the Mojo is used up, then the runestone no longer works until more Mojo is used to activate it again.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3f386971-ed11-413d-9db0-a12014f23347",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Personally speaking, if you are in a magical battle that is lasting longer than the Null runestone's spell is active, you should sincerely consider retreating from that battle. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2bbcd55a-ee44-4e74-b8f8-f03d79092e78",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It is far better to abandon your runestones and escape than to lose your life.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "c69ec45c-0d88-4a00-8300-b68e6370e498",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "68",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "27629969-9f65-474c-9239-5ec830cc93fb",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b10c9cf0-9ba8-41cb-8444-bfc1a89b5270",
                            "text": "Make a Wizard Joke",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c85765c2-e00f-477e-af8a-0633737e5635",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Why do people think Wizards who make runestones are all batty?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e62085a3-d587-4bca-87f7-655f44a9d951",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Because they are clearly <i>rune-atics!</i>",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "588e1950-6d61-44b0-9a09-dd8ca96ea2a3",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "May we please return to the topic at hand?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
